# Email

## Transactional Emails

Transactional emails are sent by the backend to a specific person and contain personalised information.

### MJML

https://mjml.io

## Marketing Emails

Sent by a 3rd party, the template and the content can be easily customised by marketing people, and are sent to many people, and do not contain personalised information.

### MailChimp

### Active Campaign
